Green planet and Red planet was connected
by mysterious power, so they met each other
But their houses are destroyed. Go Fix them.
Drag brown block
onto the blueprints
Drag the guys into
box with same color
They lost many building materials during the change
Luckly, Green and Red collected some materials back
They can now have a room.
They found a shinning green block by surprise
The Red liked it very mush, and wanted to decorate
her house. But when they moved the block to Red plannet
the block got changed!
Drag the green block to the right
Great! there were many cool blocks like this
They buit a tower to expant their view.
They saw the forest far away. The tree are weired,
But seems good enough for building.
They decided to build one house together.
It's a lot of fun with the magic blocks.
It's wonderful to feel the wind breeze
as while as standing on the colorful tower
They built an memorial for the great connection
Hey! We get so many blocks, why not build a castle!
Finally, they built a ship, it's told the ship can fly.
The Red and Green traveled to many platnets with it.
You want to know more of their advanture?
Maybe next time :P
